Background image repetition


Background image-fixed position

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>background attachment property</title>
    <style>
        body{
            width: 250px;
            height: 200px;
            overflow: scroll;
            color:yellowgreen;
            background-image: url(/CSS3/leaf.jpg);
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Scroll down the page to see the effect</h1>
